@startgantt UrbanOps - Planning type projet
printscale weekly zoom 1.2
title Diagramme de Gantt - UrbanOps

' Version compatible : integration demarre apres Backend (chemin le plus long apres conception)
[Analyse du besoin] lasts 5 days
[Conception BDD + API] lasts 7 days and starts at [Analyse du besoin]'s end
[Backend Spring Boot] lasts 14 days and starts at [Conception BDD + API]'s end
[Frontend Next.js] lasts 12 days and starts at [Conception BDD + API]'s end
[Intégration API + JWT] lasts 5 days and starts at [Backend Spring Boot]'s end
[Tests unitaires JUnit5 + JaCoCo] lasts 7 days and starts at [Intégration API + JWT]'s end
[Documentation + Swagger] lasts 4 days and starts at [Tests unitaires JUnit5 + JaCoCo]'s end

@endgantt

@startuml UrbanOps - Domaine metier (JPA)

title Diagramme de classes - Domaine metier (entites UrbanOps)

skinparam classAttributeIconSize 0

enum Role {
  CITIZEN
  ADMIN
}

enum IncidentStatus {
  OPEN
  IN_PROGRESS
  RESOLVED
}

enum Severity {
  HIGH
  MEDIUM
  LOW
}

class User {
  - Long id
  - String email
  - Role role
  ..
  autres attributs
}

class Category {
  - Long id
  - String name
  - String authorityEmail
}

class Sector {
  - Long id
  - String name
  - String city
}

class Incident {
  - Long id
  - String referenceCode
  - Severity severity
  - IncidentStatus status
  - Double latitude
  - Double longitude
  --
  + generateReferenceCode() : String
}

class Alert {
  - Long id
  - Severity severity
  - Boolean acknowledged
  --
  + acknowledge() : void
}

User ||--o{ Incident : reportedBy\n0..1 vers *
Category ||--o{ Incident : categorie\n1 vers *
Sector ||--o{ Incident : secteur\n1 vers *
Incident ||--o{ Alert : alertes\n1 vers 0..*

User ..> Role
Incident ..> IncidentStatus
Incident ..> Severity
Alert ..> Severity

note right of Incident
  Severite : AIAnalysisService
  (Gemini + fallback)
end note

@enduml

@startuml UrbanOps - Couches techniques backend

title Diagramme de classes - Architecture technique (Spring)

skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam linetype polyline

package "ma.urbanops.controller" #LightBlue {
  class AuthController
  class IncidentController
  class UserController
  class CategoryController
  class SectorController
  class StatsController
  class AlertController
}

package "ma.urbanops.service" #LightGreen {
  class IncidentService
  class UserService
  class CategoryService
  class SectorService
  class StatsService
  class AlertService
  class AIAnalysisService
